query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `notificationEngagementMetrics` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `notificationId` int NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `deliveredAt` timestamp NULL,
  `deliveryDuration` int,
  `viewedAt` timestamp NULL,
  `clickedAt` timestamp NULL,
  `actionTakenAt` timestamp NULL,
  `actionType` varchar(100),
  `dismissedAt` timestamp NULL,
  `timeToView` int,
  `timeToClick` int,
  `timeToAction` int,
  `deviceType` varchar(50),
  `browserType` varchar(50),
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (`notificationId`) REFERENCES `notificationHistory`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (`userId`) REFERENCES `users`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  INDEX `notificationId_idx` (`notificationId`),
  INDEX `userId_idx` (`userId`),
  INDEX `viewedAt_idx` (`viewedAt`),
  INDEX `clickedAt_idx` (`clickedAt`),
  INDEX `actionTakenAt_idx` (`actionTakenAt`)
)
